texts.text:
*Chuckle*
Wonderful! You are all doing so splendidly...!
Everyone, now...!
Okay!
>The water demons begin focusing their attacks on Anahita!
Unfortunately, you cannot outdo me when it comes to manipulating water... Hm?
>The water under Anahita's control begins to freeze...!

Look at you...!
Nicely done!

Liberators!
Now!
Aight, copy that! Fire at will, y'all!
Devil Download!!
*Scream*
W-We win...?
Yes, you appear to be victorious. I yield...

*Chuckle*
Your power is impressive.
I have not had that much fun in quite some time.
B-But you don't seem hurt or tired at all.
The rest of us are completely exhausted...
But it was nice to exercise a little after getting in some beauty sleep.
Also, the victor deserves to be rewarded.
Speak and I shall grant your wish.
So what is it that you wish of me?
Um... We asked you once already. You know, just after we summoned you...?
Oh, you did?
I was still sleepy, so I cannot say that I recall entirely...
Something about ground water and...?
Yo, is she really the goddess y'all wanted to summon...?
Oh, is that all?
Yes, there really is nothing quite like nice, clean water.
The malice you speak of still hangs over this place as well...
Allow me to... Purify.
>Anahita snaps her fingers and water begins to flow everywhere!
>Streams cascade into rapids as they rush through the Aura Gate...!
Wait, we won't be able to...!
Huh? We can breathe underwater...?
And these waves aren't sweeping us away for some reason.
Whoa, this is so cool! It's all so new to me!
W-What is the meaning of all this water...?!
So clean... But fierce... At this rate...
It will purify us...!!
*Scream*
>All traces of hostile demons are washed away from the Aura gate...
Yes, that should be everything...
There, all clean, including the water beneath Tokyo.
Yo, just like that...?
This is nothing.
I essentially just performed first aid on an open wound.
You understand that this is not the end, yes?
Wait, it's not over...?
Just think about it. How did this water become contaminated in the first place?
Do you expect me to cleanse the source of that impurity?
Yeah, we'd be asking too much of you...
This water will not stay clean and pure forever.
Not unless you deal with the source of this evil.
Evil... You mean human malice...?
Yes, but I did imbue this water with my power to ward off this malice.
As long as that remains in place, it will be safe.
Anahita, thank you...! How do we ever repay you for this...?!
I had my share of fun, so think of it as a little treat, on me...
More importantly.
Are you the ones who are to face Vanitas when that time comes?
Yes.
No.
My, someone seems awfully confident in themselves.
Preventing it from showing up at all would be best...
Oh, not ready for it?
Or are you trying to prevent it from showing up at all?

Hmm... But I see...
I have made my decision.
I will aid you all in whatever ways I can.
What?!
We had a little fun, you won and I rewarded you as such.
I was about to fare thee well, but...
I am fully awake now, and this is far too exciting an opportunity to pass up.
Yay! She's gonna be our friend!
I... I don't believe it...!
Yo, we sure ain't sayin' no if you're thinkin' about joinin' us.
Thank you very much!
Oh, rolling out the welcome wagon already?
I may not know what to do with myself afterwards...
So allow me to...
>Anahita goes around and taps each Liberator on their forehead.
There...
Our contract is set. Call me whenever you like.
If you ever need me, just let me know and I will be right there...
So for now, bye♡
>Anahita disappears...

No, wait...
Anahita...
Everything about her was so good. Right down to her ditziness...♡
You never cease to amaze us, Ririn.
Thank you for your help, Liberators.
Yes, we should be safe for the time being thanks to your efforts.
Nah, it's all good.
But we really can't let our guard down.
This isn't the first time evil energy made its way into the natural world.
And the Dragon Stream has everything to do with that.
A connection like that can't be undone very easily.
For better or worse, whatever happens there happens here too.
Not only that, Anahita's spell won't last forever.
She even said so herself.
Aight, that just means we gotta start workin' faster than ever.
Yo, we need to find the best way to deal with all this malice...!
And please feel free to call for our help if you ever need it.
Yeah, that includes me too!
And keep this in mind.
Demons can either be your friends or foes.
But the onus lies with you to determine which way they ultimately lean.
Yo, got it...
Aight, let's take this chance to have us a little kickoff party for our plan.

Like at...
A nice, pretty beach!
